cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, which are typically covered by the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep neural networks for learning the low-to-high resolution mapping falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also mentions remote sensing scenarios, which could be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
